!! Make caps lock and escape
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
remove Lock = Caps_Lock
keysym Caps_Lock = Escape
add Lock = Caps_Lock

!! Make Escape ` and  ~
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
keycode 9 = grave asciitilde

!! Make Home key Â£ and Caps Lock
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
keycode 110 = sterling Caps_Lock

!! Make [Alr Gr] into [mod3Mask]
!! for xmonad / i3 etc
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
clear Mod1
add Mod1    = Alt_L Meta_L
add Mod3    = Alt_R
